441
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:40,760
I am Hua Tian, the crown prince's personal guard. Greetings, Adjutant Mo.

442
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:42,660
Greetings.

443
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:45,130
