476
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:10,440
and play a scheme to let the crown prince

477
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:12,090
get caught in his own trap.

478
00:41:12,090 --> 00:41:15,100
Crown Prince is the heir.

479
00:41:15,100 --> 00:41:17,380
